Make XICOR Test Examples
================

``` r
library(XICOR)
library(yaml)

mk_vec <- function() {
  if(runif(1) < 0.5) {
    return(sample.int(n = 10, size = 20, replace = TRUE))
  } else {
    return(runif(n = 20))
  }
}

mk_example <- function(...) {
  a <- mk_vec()
  b <- mk_vec()
  
  f <- function(...) {
    calculateXI(a, b, seed=NULL)
  }
  
  xicor <- vapply(1:100, f, numeric(1))
  list(a = a, b = b, xicor = xicor)
}

examples <- lapply(1:50, mk_example)

examples
```
